::Striker::

Striker smiles as Spears wraps her hands around his neck. He looks at her 
face as she rests her head on his shoulder, activating his jetpack as he 
hears her words. He didn't want to panic her, so he wouldn't fly too high, 
but it was easier to fly a femm-bot than to walk with her in his arms.

"I won't fly too high," he says to her as his feet leave the ground, going up 
about 5 feet.
